Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,200.389)}The Monstrous Wolf Man's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Killer Party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jingle bells! Jingle bells!\NJingle all the way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jingle bells! Jingle bells!\NJingle all the way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, it's getting cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Better go, better go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Igami!\NI'm coming with you, Igami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a valuable test subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the Wolf Virus\Nhas turned him into a wolfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let this test wolfman\Nrun loose in the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider will get\Nwind of Operation: Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispose of the body at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A present for his\Nchild, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That wolfman took\Nmy doll away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:11.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H1D5913&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Wakakusa Nursery School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all good kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Santa will bring\Nthem wonderful presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather meet Kamen\NRider than Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Big Brother Taki\Nwill bring him by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You did such a nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, we've got big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On Christmas, we're gonna get a visit\Nfrom Kamen Rider instead of Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ichimonji, Mr. Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to\Nmake promises like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to disappoint\Nthem, Ms. Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're missing our\Nbrightest voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She came down with a\Nsudden fever last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That wolfman took my doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolfman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a bad man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll get a new\Ndoll for Christmas, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be hoping for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There really is a wolfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...\Nyou think I'm lying too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never lie, Kumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you get my doll\Nback from the wolfman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the dead man was bringing\Nthis doll home, but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a brand new doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a shoe with\Nit, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wakakusa Nursery\NSchool, Kumiko Hayase."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A witness, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really believe\Nthat little girl, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... the fact that she's a child\Nmakes me more inclined to believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, two men went missing\Nin this area last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think\Nthis is gonna pan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Something did happen\Nhere last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kumi happened to see it,\Nand her fear gave her a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think it was\Na wolfman she saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We came looking\Nfor a child's doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A child's doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen\Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this area is off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NSorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.95,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H1D5913&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Wakakusa Nursery School
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the children\Nall asleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I'd closed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is Kumiko's bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with Kumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us! Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumi's is... number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that...\NIt really is a wolfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...\NYou're Ichimonji and Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know our names?\NThat means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't come any closer,\Nunless you want the child to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolfman... look at that child again\Nwith those beady eyes of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf Man...\Nwhy are you kidnapping a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's killing you I'm\Nmore concerned with now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, hurry!\NTake Goro to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... he escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nthe next time we meet, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:35.90,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to Hayato,\Nwho believed that little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shocker really\Nis horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to kill a girl just\Nfor witnessing their plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wolfman was\Njust an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Kumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was too\Nscared to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kumi...\Ndid they say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything will help.\NTry to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.\NHe mentioned "Operation: Wolf."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Operation: Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency message from\NFBI headquarters in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They've decoded a\NShocker message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"At 1 PM today, a Shocker executive\Nwill arrive in Tanzai District.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's related to Operation: Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigate at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out what\NOperation: Wolf is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sure to be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Shocker for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They arrived right on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know more\Nabout Operation: Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go... of that bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This might teach us the\Nsecret of Operation: Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!\NAn invitation from Colonel Zol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're holding a party to\Nkick off Operation: Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please attend in costume."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to take them\Nup on that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the party venue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindly show me your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful to have you\Nall here at this Shocker party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity's fools are out\Nthere celebrating Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But this will be the last\NChristmas they'll ever enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Wolf will put the\Nentire world into Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, as the ultimate present\Noffered at today's Shocker party,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we will slay that perpetual\Nthorn in our side and his ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen. Remove your masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That decoy message brought\Nyou here as planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Too overwhelmed to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the FBI agent disguised\Nas his driver as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew not to trust that setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too good to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where is Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the warehouse\Nfor the Wolf Virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well?\N- I set the bombs in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the Wolf Virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol... aren't you going to\Nbring out your loyal Wolf Man henchman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you can transform\Ninto Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, can transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're...\Na cyborg, like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a Wolf Man could\Nexecute Operation: Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:20.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H1D5913&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Wakakusa Nursery School
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.26,0:22:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised he'd bring Kamen\NRider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's off doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I came, just as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this, won't you, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here, Kumi.\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker commander-in-chief Colonel Zol\Nrevealed his true form before his downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:31.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker continues to pursue\Nits ambitions of world conquest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:34.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and they will surely send\Nmore powerful enemies, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider!\NFight for peace and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.35,0:23:40.91,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:45.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:46.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We'll see a new Shocker\Nstrategist, Doctor Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:52.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the first Rider, Hongo\NTakeshi, face Snowman down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The second Rider, Ichimonji\NHayato, heads for Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:01.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Deathmatch! The Monstrous Snowman Versus\Nthe Two Riders!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:01.31,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs100\fscy90\bord.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,190.389)}Deathmatch! The Monstrous Snowman
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:01.31,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(425,429)}Versus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:01.31,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\fscy90\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,680.389)}The Two Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:10.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:12.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:14.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:17.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:20.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.13,0:24:22.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:23.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.80,0:24:25.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.69,0:24:33.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.36,0:24:36.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.94,0:24:40.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:45.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Wolf\NMan's Killer Party